detaileddescription.para: Declare a dummy CLID for xAOD::TauJetContainer_v1. This is only necessary to get DataLink<xAOD::TauJetContainer_v1> and ElementLink<xAOD::TauJetContainer_v1> compiling in the dictionary. The CLID is not needed in the "real" code, since users are never exposed to the _v1 classes in Athena anymore.
